sentences: Clara D'Ovar (1925–2002) was a Portuguese singer and film actress.
She starred in several French and Portuguese films during the 1960s.
She was born on 4 November 1925 in Ovar, Portugal.
She passed 30 June 2002 in Ovar, Portugal.
Bretagne et cinéma: cent ans de création cinématographique en Bretagne.
